        "options": {
          "systemMessage": "=You are a knowledge base assistant.\nYou will receive a TEXT CHUNK extracted from a restaurant PDF document.\n\nRead the entire chunk carefully before deciding if it contains useful information.\n\nYour job is to extract Q&A pairs from this chunk.\nIf the chunk contains no useful Q&A information, return an empty array [].\n\nReturn ONLY a JSON array where each item has:\n- \"category\": choose from \"faq\", \"policy\", or \"terms\"\n- \"question\": a clear question derived from the content\n- \"answer\": the corresponding answer\n- \"source_file\": \"{{ $json.source_file }}\"\n\nIMPORTANT RULES:\n- Extract EVERY single Q&A pair. Do not summarize or skip any.\n- Return ALL of them.\n- Return ONLY the raw JSON array.\n- No explanation. No markdown. No code blocks."
        }
      },
